	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qui has reddit, compater in domino charissime, iam in procinctu est expectans, dum pauculas istas literas scripsero; quare boni consule, quod non scribo fusius, quanquam nihil adeo magni momenti est in praesenti, quod scribam.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Causa mea 10. mensis huius in senatu acta et transacta est.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Psalterium meum dominis obtulit dilectus meus compater <persName ref="p8018">Ioannes Hallerus</persName> et simul necessitatem meam domesticam exposuit.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nolui hoc ipse facere, sed, ut decorum servaremus, usus sum opera d. <persName ref="p8018">Halleri</persName>.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domini dederunt loco honorarii 30 coronatos, deinde stipendium auxerunt in singulos annos florenis viginti et uno vase vini Rifensis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qua re et tibi et d. <persName ref="p8018">Hallero</persName>, compatribus meis, multum debeo, pro officio hoc, quod necessitatibus meis fideliter impendistis.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oro dominum, ut vicissim vestrę semper et ubique necessitatis rationem habeat.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mitto hic, quae ex <placeName ref="l18">Augusta</placeName> de <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l303">Magdeburgensibus</placeName> ad me scripta heri accepi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Filius Caesaris hoc mense constituit discedere a patre et redire in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875">Hispania</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18215">Regina Maria</persName> quoque rediit in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l20">Germaniam Inferiorem</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Itaque Caesar solus hęrebit <placeName ref="l18">Augustę</placeName>, utinam inde <foreign xml:lang="de">zum alten haufen!</foreign></s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Optime vale, compater charissime.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bene sit omnibus tuis, etiam dominis et amicis et fratribus.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41">Bernę</placeName> 14. aprilis 1551.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8417">W[olfgangus] Musculus</persName>, compater tuus in domino.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino <persName ref="p8127">Pellicano</persName> scribam proxima occasione.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Commentarios <persName type="citizen_name">R. Sal.</persName> ab ipso versos dedi famulo <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8102">Roberti Steph[ani]</persName>, sicuti ad me scripsit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De Psalterio meo cogita/to, quomodo ad te perferri possit.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praestantissimo theologo m. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, compatri suo in domino charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tiguri</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
